snippet.title: DINO MARKET - ANNOUNCEMENT TRAILER
snippet.description:
👉Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3098750/Dino_Market/

Run a cozy animal market from your desktop at your own pace. Unlock new friends, buy upgrades and automate the carts to keep all the customers happy. 

For content creators:
Twitch & Youtube integration to use it as an overlay during your live stream and play mini-games with your chat!
